## Version history convention

| Segment | When to bump |
|---------|----------------|
| PATCH (x.x.**X**) | Bug fixes, copy changes, minor UI tweaks |
| MINOR (x.**X**.0) | New features, significant UI changes |
| MAJOR (**X**.0.0) | Breaking changes, major architecture shifts |
